---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Turfing & Fencing Glasgow | AB Paving & Landscaping" description="Expert lawn turfing, artificial grass and timber fencing across Glasgow & Central Scotland. Free quotes. 20+ years experience. Fully guaranteed." hasAnnouncement={true}>
<section id="main-content" class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg" style="background-image:url('images/landscaping-4.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Fresh lawn turfing and timber fencing installation Glasgow by AB Paving"></div>
  <div class="page-hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="page-hero-content">
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › Turfing &amp; Fencing</div>
    <div class="hero-tag">Turfing &amp; Fencing Specialists</div>
    <h1>Turfing &amp;<br><em>Fencing</em></h1>
    <p>New lawns, artificial grass and secure timber fencing installed across Glasgow &amp; Central Scotland. We handle every outdoor element so your garden looks great all year round.</p>
    <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="trust-bar"><div class="trust-inner">
  <div class="trust-item"><span class="ti-icon">🏆</span><div><div class="ti-text">20+ Years Experience</div><div class="ti-sub">Glasgow &amp; Central Scotland</div></div></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><span class="ti-icon">🛡️</span><div><div class="ti-text">All Work Guaranteed</div><div class="ti-sub">Your investment protected</div></div></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><span class="ti-icon">💬</span><div><div class="ti-text">Free No-Obligation Quotes</div><div class="ti-sub">No pressure, no hidden costs</div></div></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><span class="ti-icon">⭐</span><div><div class="ti-text">5-Star Google Rated</div><div class="ti-sub">Hundreds of happy customers</div></div></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><span class="ti-icon">✓</span><div><div class="ti-text">Checkatrade Approved</div><div class="ti-sub">Vetted &amp; verified</div></div></div>
</div></div>

<section class="pad" style="background:white"><div class="container"><div class="intro-split">
  <div class="intro-text">
    <span class="s-tag">About This Service</span>
    <h2 class="s-title">A Lawn You'll Love.<br>A Fence Built to Last.</h2>
    <p>A fresh lawn and a solid, well-installed fence can completely change the feel of your outdoor space. Whether your garden is a bare mud patch or just needs a refresh, our team will have it looking fantastic in no time.</p>
    <p>We supply and lay high-quality turf suitable for Scottish conditions, prepare the ground properly and ensure your new lawn has the best possible start. For those who want low maintenance all year round, we also install premium artificial grass that looks natural and stays green whatever the weather.</p>
    <p>Our fencing team installs all types of timber fencing — from traditional closeboard panels to decorative picket fencing — using treated timber that stands up to the Scottish climate.</p>
    <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:10px">Get a Free Quote Today</a>
  </div>
  <div class="intro-img-wrap"><div class="intro-img" style="background-image:url('images/garden-2.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Fresh turf lawn installed in Glasgow garden by AB Paving and Landscaping"></div></div>
</div></div></section>

<section class="includes-sec pad"><div class="container">
  <div class="center"><span class="s-tag">What We Offer</span><h2 class="s-title">Our Turfing &amp; Fencing<br>Services</h2></div>
  <div class="includes-grid">
    <div class="inc-card"><div class="inc-icon">🌿</div><h3>Lawn Turfing</h3><p>We supply and lay premium quality turf, with full ground preparation — stripping, levelling and top soiling — so your new lawn thrives from day one.</p></div>
    <div class="inc-card"><div class="inc-icon">🏑</div><h3>Artificial Grass</h3><p>High-quality artificial grass that looks and feels real. No mowing, no mud, no brown patches — perfect for families, pets and low-maintenance gardens.</p></div>
    <div class="inc-card"><div class="inc-icon">🌳</div><h3>Closeboard Fencing</h3><p>The most popular choice for privacy and security. Solid, treated timber closeboard panels fitted to last for years in all weathers.</p></div>
    <div class="inc-card"><div class="inc-icon">📌</div><h3>Picket &amp; Decorative Fencing</h3><p>Traditional picket fencing and decorative styles to complement the front of your home and add kerb appeal.</p></div>
    <div class="inc-card"><div class="inc-icon">🔧</div><h3>Fence Repairs &amp; Replacement</h3><p>Storm damage, rotten posts, collapsed panels — we repair or fully replace damaged fencing quickly and at a fair price.</p></div>
    <div class="inc-card"><div class="inc-icon">⭐</div><h3>Ground Preparation</h3><p>Proper excavation, levelling and soil preparation are the foundation of a great lawn. We never cut corners on groundwork.</p></div>
  </div>
</div></section>

<section class="pad" style="background:var(--light)"><div class="container">
  <div class="center"><span class="s-tag">Our Work</span><h2 class="s-title">Turfing &amp; Fencing Projects</h2><p class="s-intro">A selection of turfing and fencing projects we've completed across Glasgow and Central Scotland.</p></div>
  <div class="gal-grid-pg" style="margin-top:44px">
    <div class="gal-pg-item tall" style="background-image:url('images/landscaping-4.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Garden turfing and lawn installation Glasgow by AB Paving"></div>
    <div class="gal-pg-item" style="background-image:url('images/garden-2.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Fresh turf lawn Glasgow garden makeover"></div>
    <div class="gal-pg-item" style="background-image:url('images/landscaping-1.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Landscaping and turfing project Central Scotland"></div>
    <div class="gal-pg-item" style="background-image:url('images/landscaping-2.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Garden transformation with new turf and fencing Glasgow"></div>
    <div class="gal-pg-item" style="background-image:url('images/garden-transformation.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Complete garden makeover with turfing and fencing Glasgow South Side"></div>
  </div>
</div></section>

<section class="process-sec pad"><div class="container">
  <div class="center"><span class="s-tag">How It Works</span><h2 class="s-title">Our Simple Process</h2></div>
  <div class="process-steps">
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><h3>Free Site Visit</h3><p>We visit your garden, assess the ground conditions, discuss your ideas and measure up accurately.</p></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><h3>Written Quote</h3><p>You'll receive a clear, detailed written quote with no hidden extras — just honest, competitive pricing.</p></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><h3>Professional Install</h3><p>Our team prepares the ground properly, installs your turf or fencing to the highest standard and keeps your site tidy.</p></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">4</div><h3>Enjoy Your Garden</h3><p>We complete a full clean-up, walk you through care advice and leave you with a fully guaranteed result.</p></div>
  </div>
</div></section>

<div class="why-strip"><div class="container"><div class="why-strip-inner">
  <div class="wi"><div class="wi-icon">🏆</div><div><div class="wi-title">20+ Years Experience</div><div class="wi-text">Hundreds of turfing and fencing projects across Glasgow and Central Scotland.</div></div></div>
  <div class="wi"><div class="wi-icon">💷</div><div><div class="wi-title">Competitive Pricing</div><div class="wi-text">Fair, transparent quotes with no hidden charges or surprise bills.</div></div></div>
  <div class="wi"><div class="wi-icon">✓</div><div><div class="wi-title">Checkatrade Approved</div><div class="wi-text">Vetted and verified — check our reviews before you commit.</div></div></div>
  <div class="wi"><div class="wi-icon">🛡️</div><div><div class="wi-title">Guaranteed Work</div><div class="wi-text">Every job we complete is fully guaranteed for your total peace of mind.</div></div></div>
</div></div></div>

<section class="cta-sec">
  <h2>Ready for a <span>Beautiful New Garden?</span></h2>
  <p>Get your free, no-obligation quote today. We'll visit, advise and give you a full written estimate — no pressure, no hidden costs.</p>
  <div class="cta-btns">
    <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
    <a href="tel:07492263394" class="btn-white">📞 Call 07492 263394</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="related-sec pad">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="center"><span class="s-tag">You Might Also Like</span><h2 class="s-title">Our Other Services</h2></div>
    <div class="related-grid">
      <a href="/block-paving-driveways" class="rel-card">
        <div class="rel-img" style="background-image:url('images/hero-driveway.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Block paving driveway Glasgow by AB Paving"></div>
        <div class="rel-body"><h3>Block Paving Driveways</h3><p>Stunning block paving driveways that add kerb appeal and real value to your home.</p><span class="rel-link">Learn More →</span></div>
      </a>
      <a href="/patios-slabbing" class="rel-card">
        <div class="rel-img" style="background-image:url('images/patio-1.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Patio and slabbing Glasgow by AB Paving"></div>
        <div class="rel-body"><h3>Patios &amp; Slabbing</h3><p>Beautiful patios in natural stone, porcelain and sandstone — designed for outdoor living.</p><span class="rel-link">Learn More →</span></div>
      </a>
      <a href="/walls-brickwork" class="rel-card">
        <div class="rel-img" style="background-image:url('images/landscaping-3.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Walls and brickwork Glasgow by AB Paving"></div>
        <div class="rel-body"><h3>Walls &amp; Brickwork</h3><p>Retaining walls, garden steps and decorative brickwork built to last in Scottish weather.</p><span class="rel-link">Learn More →</span></div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
